Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.04,0:00:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女教师优子男人的初次性体验\N性教育指导
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.12,0:00:52.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,围绕你的是天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.28,0:00:55.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们一直在那里指导着你的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.36,0:01:02.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你软弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.16,0:01:06.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请求力量 \N那么她们会赐予你力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.72,0:01:12.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她们是你的护身符
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.04,0:01:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家听我讲课吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.76,0:01:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在听呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.36,0:01:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是\N意思不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.56,0:01:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家稍微变得可爱点可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.64,0:01:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可爱?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.88,0:01:41.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还有别的事情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.12,0:01:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.28,0:01:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,河泽\N去哪里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.12,0:02:20.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,课间时间去哪里\N跟你没关保吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.88,0:02:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就职于这所学校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.44,0:02:30.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.96,0:02:36.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天还继续拍吗\N好累啊  不去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.28,0:02:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一会去哪里呢\N又是游戏厅啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.28,0:02:44.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没钱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.08,0:02:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前次赢了呢\N又去玩游戏啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.72,0:02:56.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去唱歌吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.95,0:02:57.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让学生们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.88,0:03:02.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重新振作起来\N激起了我的兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.96,0:03:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是\N那个想法还没有一点头绪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.28,0:03:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去唱歌吧\N选择便宜的套餐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.52,0:03:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意大利面包\N之前吃过的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.84,0:04:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,河泽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.36,0:04:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么没去学校呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.72,0:04:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橄榄球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.04,0:04:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,河泽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.60,0:04:26.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来是选手呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.36,0:04:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.80,0:04:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,团队就我一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.56,0:04:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.44,0:04:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是\N老师为什么在这里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.20,0:04:48.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人吃饭有意思吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.56,0:04:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被欺负了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.48,0:05:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前身体很弱\N经常受欺负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.32,0:05:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是只要听话\N就可以和平相处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.48,0:05:09.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡说什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.20,0:05:13.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不叫朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.76,0:05:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.36,0:05:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.96,0:06:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,河泽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.28,0:06:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们玩橄榄球吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.08,0:06:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要河泽\N交到真正的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.52,0:06:21.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时让朋友们加入橄榄球队\N把橄榄球发扬光大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.04,0:06:27.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的内心有了这个想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.96,0:07:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家听我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.88,0:07:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家想跟老师玩橄榄球吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.24,0:07:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要啊\N好土
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.56,0:07:26.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家没有奋斗的目标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.88,0:07:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天过日子不充实吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.24,0:07:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么叫做浪费时间啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.92,0:07:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.68,0:07:40.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人生真的很短暂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.28,0:07:44.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为这样\N才需要有激情的斗志啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.40,0:07:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长大后\N不管发生什么苦难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.04,0:07:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想起自己\N曾经奋斗过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.84,0:07:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个激情的斗志啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.64,0:08:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师也会加油的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.48,0:08:10.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪你们一起走下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.04,0:08:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们玩橄榄球吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.52,0:08:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都做吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.44,0:08:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别骗人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.64,0:08:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是真心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.76,0:08:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然这样的话\N真的什么都肯做吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.76,0:08:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话\N在这里自慰试试啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.40,0:08:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡说什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.08,0:08:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别乱说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.56,0:08:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太勉强老师了呢\N估计做不到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.76,0:09:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里我要是拒绝的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.64,0:09:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.48,0:09:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师\N不用勉强自己啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.32,0:09:57.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.48,0:10:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.00,0:10:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相反的是\N进入橄榄球队啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.24,0:10:15.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们说好了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.04,0:10:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.20,0:10:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会玩真的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.28,0:10:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好丰满啊\N真的好丰满啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.12,0:10:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要自慰吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.04,0:10:41.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会玩真的吧\N要不妙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.04,0:10:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真大啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.64,0:11:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好性感啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.32,0:11:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去一边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.92,0:11:25.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好性感啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.96,0:11:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次看到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.72,0:11:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是第一次呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.20,0:11:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离好近啊\N好性感呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.08,0:11:45.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己抚摸小穴呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.40,0:11:50.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己抚摸小穴呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.16,0:11:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抚摸阴蒂啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.36,0:12:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被发现真不妙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.84,0:12:13.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.44,0:12:18.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抚摸的好兴奋呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.68,0:12:21.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着我好入神呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.00,0:12:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看的好清楚呢\N爽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.28,0:12:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他距离好近呢\N真的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.12,0:12:54.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉要看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.20,0:12:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乳头快要看到了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.56,0:13:01.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乳头真好看\N粉色呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.44,0:13:08.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真漂亮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.20,0:13:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好柔软的样子呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.12,0:13:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次看到女人的乳头呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.08,0:13:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好兴奋啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.96,0:13:31.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姿势真性感啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.72,0:13:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乳头变硬了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.84,0:14:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.04,0:14:08.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉要看到了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.88,0:14:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师兴奋了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.04,0:14:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师发出了色情色情的声音呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.68,0:15:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不好啊\N全部看到了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.32,0:15:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.24,0:15:27.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小穴看到了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.92,0:15:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想舔舔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.48,0:16:09.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.04,0:16:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味道不秒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.60,0:16:34.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师超级兴奋了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.40,0:17:03.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.60,0:17:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加入橄榄球队\N好好训练的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.04,0:17:14.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来自慰之外的事情\N也是可以做到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.20,0:17:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还会有别的事情\N什么意思呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.64,0:17:25.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还会有别的事情\N什么意思呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.04,0:17:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的可以吗\N学生们的心里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.28,0:17:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传达到心里的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.52,0:17:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要丢掉面子\N卸掉所有的包袱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.40,0:17:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能互相面对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.12,0:17:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好心里的准备了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.00,0:17:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.44,0:17:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问题如堆山之高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.84,0:17:47.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有一位学生离开了我的视线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.16,0:17:49.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山田的情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.24,0:17:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.92,0:18:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,数日后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.52,0:18:16.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做不到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.56,0:18:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,队长是河择
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.12,0:18:23.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最初就是决定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.64,0:18:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做不到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.08,0:18:26.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.56,0:18:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到这几天的训练后\N你心里有数了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.24,0:18:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明没有能力做队长啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.08,0:18:51.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.16,0:19:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是即便如此\N队长还是河泽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.92,0:19:03.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非你莫属啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.96,0:19:06.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.24,0:19:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是队长的\N没有人愿意跟随我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.32,0:19:17.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你比淮都有\N对橄榄球的热爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.16,0:19:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.24,0:19:24.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人坚持到现在了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.24,0:19:29.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是\N我真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.72,0:19:32.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么\N对自己没信心呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.64,0:19:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这说自己呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.00,0:19:38.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对自己要有信心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.88,0:19:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会受欢迎的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.48,0:19:41.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能受欢迎呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.24,0:19:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是受欺负\N被人无视的人生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.60,0:19:57.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是为了改变现在的自己吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.52,0:20:00.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.68,0:20:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师给你自信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.56,0:20:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.16,0:20:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.36,0:21:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
