Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:13.28,1:11:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夜晚的废弃物\N打架的山田
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:18.08,1:11:21.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加上之前的种种行窃
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:23.04,1:11:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,校长说了\N再有下次直接退学
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:29.12,1:11:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:38.88,1:11:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别以为跟我一起道歉\N我就得感谢你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:45.12,1:11:46.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没这个想法
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:49.12,1:11:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:50.88,1:11:52.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证过
