Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:28.16,1:12:31.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我赢了\N人部
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:35.52,1:12:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比赛胜负?
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:37.92,1:12:39.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算干什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:40.00,1:12:42.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会打女人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:42.88,1:12:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡说什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:47.84,1:12:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:50.40,1:12:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:10.08,1:13:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算干什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:17.60,1:13:19.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为教师
