Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:01.76,1:14:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是傻瓜\N做什么都可以呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:13.92,1:14:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
